snippet.title: You haven't watched funnier: ANIMALS & KIDS - Only the best REACTIONS and FAILS!
snippet.description:
Animals and kids can be awesome; mixing these two together will make your day! This compilations is a collection of ONLY the BEST clips we could find. Cats, dogs, donkeys, frogs and much more other animals + our awesome KIDS!! So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

The content in this compilation is licensed and used with authorization of the rights holder. If you have any questions about compilation or clip licensing, please contact us: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun

MUSIC:
"Hammrock Fight, Fluffing a Duck, Feeling Good, Aunt Tagonist, Monkeys Spinnin Monkeys" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
